            "title": "Variables",
            "id": 76142,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Les variables sont appelées variables parce que les valeurs qu'elles stockent peuvent changer. Nous pouvons mettre à jour <code>status</code> en utilisant <code>=</code> et en lui donnant une nouvelle valeur.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"status = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Watching Netflix&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"status = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Relaxing at the beach&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(status)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"35\" endIndex=\"36\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\":\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Relaxing at the beach\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>=</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "As often as we want",
            "id": 76143,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Nous pouvons mettre à jour les variables aussi souvent que nous le souhaitons. Essaie-le toi-même : change la valeur de <code>status</code> en <code>\"New data required\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"status = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Incomplete&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"status = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Complete&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(status)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"status = \" /><text value=\"&quot;New data required&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(status)\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"57\" endIndex=\"63\" /><option startIndex=\"64\" endIndex=\"65\" /><option startIndex=\"66\" endIndex=\"85\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Complete\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"New data required\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>status</code> suivi de <code>=</code> et enfin <code>\"New data required\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
